      "content": "hey, i just got in from my flight to tokyo and i feel kinda weird. my left arm feels really heavy and kind of tingly, like it's falling asleep. also my voice sounds a bit thick when i talk. do u think i'm just exhausted from the long trip? maybe i just need some water and a nap",
